        <title>Frontity JS Module File</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Johan]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>The reason that that file is so big is because you merged all files together, JS, CSS (CSS-in-JS) and probably fonts as well.</p>
<p>A simple solution is to use <a href="https://docs.frontity.org/performance/code-splitting" class="inline-onebox" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Code Splitting - Frontity Docs</a> which will cut the file in smaller pieces.</p>
